To Allah belong the east and the west; so wherever you turn, there is the Face of Allah; surely Allah is All-Embracing, All-Knowing.
And they say: Allah has taken a son. Glory be to Him! Glory be to Him, all that is in the heavens and on earth: all are all surrendered to Him.
The Originator of the heavens and the earth, and when He decrees a matter, He says to it, "Be," and it is.
And those who do not know say, "Why does Allah not speak to us, or not come to us with a sign?" But those before them said, "Their hearts are like those who were before them. We have indeed explained the signs for people who believe."
