And wherever you are, turn your face towards the Sacred Mosque, and wherever you are, turn your faces to the Sacred Mosque, so that you may not have any argument against any other people except those of them who do wrong, so fear them, and I will complete My favor upon you, so that I may complete My favor upon you and that you may be guided.
Just as We have sent among you a Messenger from yourselves reciting to you Our verses and purifies you and teaching you the Book and wisdom, and teaching you that which you did not know.
